{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_01_01",
  "title": "『劇団★見』\n旗揚げ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、今日は誘ってくれてありがとう！\nトリエルが主演の舞台、凄く面白かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ thanks for inviting us today!\nThe play starring TRINITYAiLE was really amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.977301216299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.1839678448
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "演出も凝っていて見応えがあったわね。三人とも\n格好良かったし、悪役のfranさんもハマってたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The direction was elaborate and very engaging. All three of them\nwere so cool‚ and fran-san fit the villain role perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1839678448,
      "endTime": 17.4839678449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.6773011209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "2.5次元舞台『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』……\n私も初演を観た時は感動した。今回は待望の第二弾……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The 2.5D stage play \"Pretty★Angel\"…\nI was moved when I saw the first run. This time was the long-awaited sequel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6773011209,
      "endTime": 26.6264395715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 26.8131063145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんは表現力が豊か……体は小さいのに\nとっても大きく見えた……まさに天才子役……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan’s expressiveness was incredible… even though she’s small‚\nshe looked so commanding… truly a genius child actress…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8131063145,
      "endTime": 34.99868447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 35.2120178224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは、さすが大女優の娘……標準語のセリフも\n完璧で……あの演技力はきっと天性のもの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan really is the daughter of a great actress… even her standard Japanese lines\nwere flawless… that acting talent must be innate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2120178224,
      "endTime": 43.8037410737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さんは存在感が凄くて後光が差して見えた……\nこれが主役の貫禄……推しは舞台でも最高だった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-san’s presence was overwhelming—she practically glowed…\nThat’s the dignity of a lead role… my favorite was amazing even on stage…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.003740883,
      "endTime": 52.8870729449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.1004060111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "franさんは言わずもがな……悪の四天王『ネクロ』\nをあそこまで忠実かつ大胆に表現出来るのは彼女だけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And fran-san goes without saying… only she could portray\nthe Evil Four’s “Necro” with that level of faithfulness and boldness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1004060111,
      "endTime": 62.3004056296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.5070721628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "演劇の感想なのに\nドルオタの推し語りに聞こえるのはどうしてかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though this is supposed to be a theater review‚\nwhy does it sound like an idol fan gushing about her favorite?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.5070721628,
      "endTime": 68.1470723154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 68.3404054961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "舞台、大変そうだけど……いつかやってみたい……\nトリエルのお芝居を観て、そう思った……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stage acting looks tough‚ but… I’d like to try it someday…\nWatching TRINITYAiLE’s performance made me feel that way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3404054961,
      "endTime": 76.6631716095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 76.8498381617
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "同感だよ！\n私も舞台をやりたい熱がメラメラ燃え上がってるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same!\nMy desire to do stage acting is blazing right now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8498381617,
      "endTime": 83.1998383523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 83.4065050763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら、舞台のお仕事を受けられないか\n{user}さんに相談してみたら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that’s the case‚ why not ask {user}-san\nwhether you could take on stage work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4065050763,
      "endTime": 89.2148268385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12060.1603188
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.4148269338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……やる気アピールは大事……\n早速メッセでお願いしてみる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… showing motivation is important…\nI’ll try asking by message right away…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4148269338,
      "endTime": 95.2666653951,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8433.2429249
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.8480698587
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もう返事がきた……「やる気は伝わってきたが\n演技経験なしでいきなり舞台の仕事は難しい」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there’s already a reply… “I can feel your enthusiasm‚ but\njumping straight into stage work without acting experience would be difficult”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5333320618,
      "endTime": 110.18333244339999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.4114002547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "むぅ……私にも演技の経験くらい、ある……\n小学生の時に、劇で木の役をやった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmph… I do have acting experience…\nWhen I was in elementary school‚ I played a tree in a play…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4114002547,
      "endTime": 118.81140063609999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "舞台の上で、無言のまま微動だにしない……\nあの瞬間、私は木になりきっていた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Standing silently on stage‚ not moving an inch…\nIn that moment‚ I truly became a tree…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0247337979,
      "endTime": 126.7156634967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 123.23332901
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 126.9289966584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……確かに演劇の経験ではあるけれど\n演技の経験と言えるかは難しいところかも？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is… technically stage experience‚ but\nwhether it counts as acting experience is debatable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9289966584,
      "endTime": 135.9009469987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 136.1009470941
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、経験がないからって\nやっちゃいけない訳じゃないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But just because you don’t have experience\ndoesn’t mean you’re not allowed to try‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1009470941,
      "endTime": 141.22530078900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.438634046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "大事なのは本人のやる気だよ\n本気でやりたいと思ってるかどうかだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What matters is your motivation.\nWhether you truly want to do it or not!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.438634046,
      "endTime": 147.6714686711,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14728.031349100007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.8581353188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんの言う通り……私は本気！　誰でも最初は\n初心者……今度は電話で直接、熱意をぶつけてみる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan is right… I’m serious! Everyone starts as\na beginner… This time‚ I’ll call and tell him my passion directly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.8581353188,
      "endTime": 157.2996767998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 157.8996706963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、{user}さん？　さっきの話\n私は本気……トリエルの舞台を観て、感じた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san? About what we discussed earlier—\nI’m serious… Watching TRINITYAiLE’s stage play made me realize…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8996706963,
      "endTime": 167.2396706582,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.4263372105
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
